# TAPPS Quality Pipeline

This project uses the TAPPS MCP server for code quality enforcement. TappsMCP is provided by **MCP_DOCKER** (Docker MCP Toolkit); configure `.cursor/mcp.json` and, for headless/auto-bugfix, `.mcp.json` at project root. See [.cursor/MCP_SETUP_INSTRUCTIONS.md](../MCP_SETUP_INSTRUCTIONS.md).

## Session Start (REQUIRED)

Call `tapps_session_start()` as the FIRST action in every session.

## After Editing Python Files (REQUIRED)

Call `tapps_quick_check(file_path)` after editing any Python file.

